Quote:  He sells more than 200 Bankdam rams a year, including some to Paul Bowen's Agridome Show in Rotorua and Japan, where they parade daily as examples of top-quality New Zealand Romneys... The Bankdam Romney provided a strong base, and he added East Friesian for milk, fertility and growth, Poll Dorset for carcass structure and also for milk, fertility and growth, and for toughness he put in the Cheviot....
